        "when": "2026-02",
        "text": "She does great work and is really friendly. Her website does have more of a wedding photo vibe, but don't discount her based on that. We did family photos with absurd wind and the photos still came out great! She is also very flexible. We showed up on the originally scheduled day and it was overcast and sprinkling and she was really cool about rescheduling. She is definitely in it for the craft! 10 out of 10 would recommend!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2020-08",
        "text": "From our engagement pictures to wedding pictures, Jennifer went above and beyond and we couldn’t be happier with the outcome of all of our pictures! Plus her communication and personality were spot on and I just loved working with her!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-09",
        "text": "Jennifer is the most professional and BEST photographer! I have never felt so beautiful in my ENTIRE life!!! She captured every moment I could have wanted!! I relived the whole wedding and reception through the photographs! I will always use her as my photographer!! 10/10 RECOMMEND!!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2019-12",
        "text": "Jennifer Garza is THE wedding, family and senior photographer for your family's needs.  She is prompt with communication, professional at all times, and makes you so relaxed when taking pictures.  She takes all the stress out and just lets you have FUN!  I will be using her for all of my family's special occasions!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2021-01",
        "text": "Jennifer Garza was an amazing wedding photographer and did an excellent job at capturing our day. She put in the extra time and effort up front to make sure we had a solid plan and had back-up location plans for things like our first look and family shots. She was calm and collected with us during the hectic getting ready morning, and made sure we were staying on-schedule. She did a great job wranging everyone for our family shots, and helped coordinate photos at each guest table. Our photos were so beautiful and we had so many! She also made sure to capture all the details of the day, including all our our rings, my dress, the table settings and decorations, etc. She captured a beautifully artistic photo of my father during his speach, and that photo made me cry! Overall, Jennifer was wonderful to work with before, during, and after the wedding. I highly recommend her!"
      }
